_sText: Welcome to The Desert Arena! A Frag-Festive Deathmatch style map with loads of Vantage Points, Hiding Spots, and Detail! Prepare to immerse yourself into a world of intense gameplay! Featuring 2 Bombsites, Sniper Points, Ramps, Catwalks, and everything you wish you had for a Paintball Arena! Keep your head up in this one... you never know where your enemy may be lurking!
